text: Heliophanus xanthopes is a jumping spider species in the genus Heliophanus. It was first described by Wanda Wesołowska in 2003 and lives in Ethiopia. ==References== Category:Spiders described in 1986 Category:Fauna of Ethiopia Category:Salticidae Category:Spiders of Africa Category:Taxa named by Wanda Wesołowska
title: Heliophanus xanthopes
